::Havoc/Repressor::

Havoc frowns, looking around and not seeing Chaos and Minion 
approaching. He'd have to talk to them about following orders later.

"It doesn't look like Chaos and Minion will be joining us," he says, 
turning to the door and entering the training room, "So we'll train 
by ourselves."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Repressor follows Havoc, surprised at Chaos and Minion's lack of 
dicipline.
